      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BACKBURN BLUEY (1) has a strong record this trip with five wins and eight placings from 15 starts. Missed the frame latest (30.87) when seventh over 520m at Q Parklands in a Grade 5. With a clean break looks hard to beat. ENTER WARP SPEED (2) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by 3.5 lengths (16.42) at this track. Capable of going close again. MR. MARVELLOUS (3) looks close to win after hitting the frame last run (20.01) at Capalaba in a Grade 3/4. Has first look at box 3 this time. Has a good record here including three wins. Hard to beat again. NINA SIYAN (7) has strong credentials at this circuit over this journey.",
